Come on! DJ, let's go!

01:21:55.670 --> 01:21:57.993
Come on, Jamie, come on.

01:21:58.073 --> 01:22:00.076
- We're almost there.
- I can't keep going.

01:22:00.175 --> 01:22:02.631
I don't think anyone's coming.
It's okay. Come on.

01:22:02.711 --> 01:22:05.191
- I can't do it.
- All right, come on.

01:22:06.681 --> 01:22:07.682
Come on, Jamie.

01:22:09.417 --> 01:22:10.418
Stop!

01:22:11.419 --> 01:22:13.865
Come on.

01:22:14.756 --> 01:22:17.293
- Come here! No! Stop!
- Please!

01:22:27.502 --> 01:22:28.537
Get off!

01:22:29.404 --> 01:22:31.247
DJ, look out!

01:22:35.543 --> 01:22:39.423
No, please! Jamie!

01:22:45.587 --> 01:22:48.693
DJ! Are you okay?

01:22:49.524 --> 01:22:50.969
I'm fine.

01:22:55.964 --> 01:22:57.637
Leave us alone!

01:22:57.732 --> 01:23:00.088
Why are you doing this to us?

01:23:00.168 --> 01:23:02.444
<i>Why are you doing this to us?</i>

01:23:02.537 --> 01:23:04.744
<i>Why are you doing this to us?</i>

01:23:12.480 --> 01:23:15.950
<i>Why are you doing this to me?</i>

01:23:17.118 --> 01:23:20.156
<i>The rules have always been very simple.</i>

01:23:20.588 --> 01:23:21.965
What is this?

01:23:22.424 --> 01:23:26.167
<i>Kill or be killed.</i>

01:23:43.445 --> 01:23:46.483
<i>It's your turn now, Jamie.</i>

01:23:48.516 --> 01:23:52.487
<i>We're not going to hurt your brother...</i>

01:23:52.587 --> 01:23:56.228
<i>As long as you do exactly what I tell you.</i>

01:23:56.858 --> 01:23:59.236
Don't listen to him, Jamie.

01:24:00.528 --> 01:24:03.532
<i>You will provide the excitement</i>

01:24:03.631 --> 01:24:06.305
<i>for our next family, Jamie.</i>

01:24:10.505 --> 01:24:14.476
<i>You will give the audience the reason</i>

01:24:20.949 --> 01:24:23.429
<i>to keep watching.</i>

